metadata.name: Rad Impressions #1
metadata.description:
Rad Impressions generates abstract sculptures by imprinting repeated geometric shapes into soft virtual surfaces. The scenes are rendered with a special raymarching system exploring a range of conditions and parameters. The interplay of form and shadow evoke a sense of movement and rhythm, revealing how impressions can change when viewed in different lights.
